# Zafora Frontend Architecture

Live urls: https://zafora-holdings-web.replit.app/
Stack: **Next.js 16 App Router** + **React 19** + Express API (`NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`) + **Tailwind CSS 4** + shadcn/Radix + **Zod** + **Server Actions** + **Axios** + **TanStack Query** + **Zustand**.

